feature_bullets: Renewed products look and work like new. name: Kids Tablet, 10 inch Tablet for Kids Android 12 Tablet 2GB 64GB Toddler Tablet APP Preinstalled & Parent Control Kids Education Children Tablet with WiFi, 8000mAh batery, Dual Camera, Netflix, YouTube
feature_bullets: 【Android 12.0 / 2GB + 64GB】This kids tablet is the latest Android 12 system, 2GB RAM and 64GB storage, running stably. This android tablet 10 inch has passed the GMS certification, You can also download apps like Youtube, Netflix, Disney+, ABCmouse etc, from Google Play. Appropriate Age Grade Over 3 years old kids,【Parental Control Mode】Android 12 tablet is specially designed for kids with the iWawa Kids app for music, drawing, learning, stories, calculations, games and more. Parents can set separate profiles for each kid, add or block apps, set screen time limits, and lock their kids tablets,【HD 10" large screen】Large 10 inch tablet, 1280*800 IPS FHD touchscreen, high contrast ratio, wide viewing angle, bright display and vivid colors. To provide children with a perfect visual experience,【Large Battery Capacity】The 8000mAh battery and low-power CPU enhance your experience and allows you to enjoy up to 8 hours of reading, watching shows, surfing the web. tablet for kids suitable for long-distance flights or road trips. Wonderful companion to your kids for playing and learning,【5-year Warranty】Whether it is Christmas or birthday gift, Kids tablet is the gift for children, And kids tablet offers a 5-year warranty and Lifetime customer service, we will provide you with a satisfactory solution within 24h. Package includes: 1 x Tablet PC, 1 x Protective Silicon

name: CHUWI HiPad X Tablet,4G LTE Unlocked Phablet,10.1 inch T618 Octa Core 6GB 128GB Android 11.0 Phone Call Tablets Dual Band WiFi Bluetooth 5.0, IPS 2K screenwith Keyboard
feature_bullets: ✔ 10.1 Inch 2K Vividness Display——The 10.1 inches 1920*1200 resolution IPS OGS screen delivers vivid vision and wider visual experience.Metal Uni-body and 2.5D curved glass make it more exquisite and premium.,✔ Play Faster, Work Better——A detachable docking keyboard turn your tablet into a PC. The equipped Android Office Software also let you can work.1024 pressure levels HiPen H3 make you feel more responsive and natural on 2K screen.,✔ M618 Octa Core Processor——The M618 is clocked at 2.4GHz with the 2*A75 cores, along with the powerful Mali G52 3EE GPU. It is one of the most fast and efficiently advanced android SoC.,✔ 4G LTE Phone Call——HiPad X supports 4G LTE with dual SIM, which connects you to cellular data networks everywhere, always free to catch up on your favorite show during your commute or trip.,✔ Double Acoustic Chamber Bring Stereoscopic Sound——The double acoustic chamber design of HiPad X makes the sound louder and stereoscopic,bringing you unparalleled experience whether watching videoes or listening to music.

Packaging and accessories may be generic. name: Amazon Fire HD 8 Plus tablet, 8” HD Display, 32 GB, 30% faster processor, 3GB RAM, wireless charging, (2022 release), Gray
feature_bullets: Fire HD 8 Plus offers everything you get with a Fire HD 8 and more - wireless charging, 9W power adapter, 3 GB RAM, 2 MP front-facing and 5 MP rear-facing cameras. New design is thinner and lighter than previous gen and has a screen made with strengthened aluminosilicate glass. As measured in tumble tests, Fire HD 8 Plus is twice as durable as Apple iPad mini (2021).,Fast and responsive - Enhanced hexa-core processor for more responsive performance (up to 30% faster than previous gen Fire HD 8 Plus) so you can get more done. Check email, tackle your to-do lists, browse the web, and more.,Use Show Mode to transform your tablet into an immersive, full-screen Alexa experience, optimized for visibility across the room. To go hands-free with Alexa, just ask Alexa to show news, check the weather, view camera feeds, make a video call, set alarms, control your smart home or play your favorite videos and music, and much more.,Great for on-the-go - Up to 13 hours of reading, browsing the web, watching videos, and listening to music. Hassle-free wireless charging dock (dock not included) offers easy charging anywhere. Choose from 32GB or 64GB (up to 1TB of expandable storage via microSD card).,Relax and unwind with your favorite content from Netflix, Facebook, Hulu, Instagram, TikTok, and more through Amazon’s Appstore (Google Play not supported. Subscription for some apps required).,Stay connected with friends and family - Ask Alexa to make video calls or download apps like Zoom.,Great for the whole family - Amazon Kids offers easy-to-use parental controls on Fire tablets. Subscribe to Amazon Kids+ for access to thousands of books, popular apps and games, videos, songs, Audible books, and more.

feature_bullets: 【Newest kids Tablet 】Kids Tablet 7 Inch comes with the most powerful Android 11 operating system equipped with quad-core processor,which makes apps run smoother. 2GB RAM, 32GB ROM, expandable up to 128GB, can store more videos, photos and music for your kids.,【Easy to Use Parental Control】Kids tablet with parental control function,which let parents to set separate profiles for each kid,add or block apps, filter contents, set screen time, lock learning tablet, even monitor activities to protect against your kids to access any unsafe contents. It can be adjusted as kids grow with content according to their age.Really convenient for any age parents, grandma, and grandpa.,【Multi Age-appropriate Contents】Our 7 inch android kids tablet comes with plenty of kids learning apps,which give kids access to thousands of free apps, games, videos, E-books. These contents can stimulate kids' imagination, creativity and self-confidence. With our tablet kids will immersed in the ocean of knowledge safely and give parents a peace of mind.,【Safety Eye Protection Screen】7 inch tablet for kids equipt with a good quality 1024x600 IPS HD display screen,clear bright screen provides outstanding visual experience,plus the screen's automatic brightness adjustment,which can better protect children's eyes.,【Best Gifts For Your Kids】: This tablet is suitable for all boys and girls,a good companion for children's study and entertainment.Our tablet for kids offers worry free warranty and lifetime customer service. We are here to answer any questions about this kids tablet 24 hours. Perfect for gifting your children on any holiday.
